A multidisciplinary, multifaceted team is the perfect match to STARME.IO's project. We care about wellness and work to share it through an innovative project: the perfect tool to keep record of techniques, practice and experience and to share knowledge anywhere, anytime you desire.This is important to us:
we believe in KNOWLEDGE should be universal, especially in the health sector;
we believe in COOPERATION as sharing information and connecting with different professionals is the path toward the future;
we believe in holistic approach BEYOND the actual DUALISM of standardization vs personalization, of mind vs heart, of science vs art;
we believe in EFFICIENCY to strive to best medical result.
It is our dream to CHANGE THE WORLD OF HEALTH THROUGH SHARING AND CONNECTING. If you care you share! Our ProjectStarMe.io is an Integrated Web Platform and Professional App. It is going to start as an App for Health Operators, starting from Kinesiologists, but its goals are way beyond that. Everyone of us can be part of StarMe.io and benefit from it!A Service for Health OperatorsStarMe.io is an app for professional work: patient records, work organization, statistics and much more. With a simple and rapid user interface StarMe.io gives you access to the best techniques available, ready to be used in your professional work.A Showcase for your ActivityContinuous improvement is the key to personal and professional achievements and discoveries. Starme.io gives you the possibility to advertise your activity and to share it with a community of professionals. Reach out to a community of peers, keen for more knowledge and more understanding.A Support for Schools and AssociationsHealth education is the key to the well being of every individual. Education comes from training and knowledge. Starme.io supports schools and associations to advertise courses and educational programs. With a selected audience of professionals, Starme.io offers you just the right community for your activities.A Common LanguageCooperation and connection are keys to personal, professional and social development. But A a Common Language is necessary! Starme.io's blog and dictionary, its procedures and techniques can be modified and approved by the Starme.io community of professionals. Starme.io is the platform for sharing and building a common path for understanding.A New Source of RevenueStarme.io rewards every contributor to the platform! If you have a new life-changing technique you want to share and spread to the world, you have come to the right place: add the technique to our database and we are going to reward you based on its use in our community.And Much MoreStarme.io's goals are wide ranging and new projects are already starting up from this platform. From publications of the most interesting statistics of the platform, through new courses and educational projects and even to the organization of clinics, Starme.io is a brand that aims to deeply change the way we consider health. It's your time NOW to make the difference and build up with us YOUR future HEALTH dimension.If you care you share! What We Need & What You GetWe offer you not just to be part of a project raising world best vibrations but also we give you the opportunity to reserve yourself a lifetime access to the knowledge created in our system or just create the best new world to come.To make it happen we would need to raise at least $ 30,000. This would cover initial IT and management costs to release the product on the market.Great perks are available too!!First of all, supporters are going to show on STARME.IO's website and in our Hall of Fame in our new head offices. More than that, you are going to be able to choose either to receive the SPECIAL EDITION STARME.IO'S T-SHIRT...Or... the magnificent STARME.IO'S HOODIE!And, last but not least, you can even get the access to one of our Operator's Packages, with the possibility to get a Lifetime access to our platform. Aren't you curios to know how it is going to grow?If you care you share! Who We Are
